{"name":"Monstrous Transformation!","type":"effect","system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>A creature who reaches @UUID[Compendium.drakkenheim-adventure-module-for-pathfinder-2nd-edition.dodrakkenheim-effects.so17g2EB1xH8JzI9]{Contaminated} level 6 or higher triggers a transformation into a horric monster controlled by the Game Master. Once triggered, the transformation finishes in 1 round. It is thereafter permanent.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.835,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2023-06-12T11:43:24.098-04:00","version":{"schema":0.796,"foundry":"10.291","system":"4.10.4"}}},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"common"},"level":{"value":1},"duration":{"value":-1,"unit":"unlimited","sustained":false,"expiry":"turn-start"},"start":{"value":0,"initiative":null},"target":null,"tokenIcon":{"show":true},"badge":null,"context":null,"unidentified":false},"img":"modules/drakkenheim-adventure-module-for-pathfinder-2nd-edition/artwork/icons/effects/MonstrousTransformation_Icon.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.nDyezXfnqb0n476R"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.10.4","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1666930364663,"modifiedTime":1686957895283,"lastModifiedBy":"NZsmhzO5jgDe7jrT"},"ownership":{"default":0,"NZsmhzO5jgDe7jrT":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"GzQbOOQ3WxgcioOd"}
{"name":"Quarry","type":"effect","system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>A creature has marked you as it's prey. The creature knows the direction and distance to its quarry as long as the quarry remains within Drakkenheim or until the creature is destroyed.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.835,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2023-06-12T11:43:27.819-04:00","version":{"schema":0.796,"foundry":"10.291","system":"4.10.4"}}},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"common"},"level":{"value":2},"duration":{"value":-1,"unit":"encounter","sustained":false,"expiry":"turn-start"},"start":{"value":0,"initiative":null},"target":null,"tokenIcon":{"show":false},"badge":null,"context":null,"unidentified":false},"img":"modules/drakkenheim-adventure-module-for-pathfinder-2nd-edition/artwork/icons/effects/Quarry_Icon.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.AV1Qc4FGpPkPMJiG"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.10.4","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1667016559793,"modifiedTime":1686957943416,"lastModifiedBy":"NZsmhzO5jgDe7jrT"},"ownership":{"default":0,"NZsmhzO5jgDe7jrT":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"MCLduKCumrqHrW4U"}
{"name":"Recharge","type":"effect","system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>Recharge is always accompanied by a value (like X) or a range (like X-Y). A creature can use a recharge ability once and then that ability cannot be used again for a number of rounds. The ability then has a random chance of recharging during each subsequent round of combat. At the start of each of the creature's turns, roll a d6. If the roll is one of the numbers in the recharge notation, the creature regains the use of the special ability.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.835,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2023-06-12T11:43:29.536-04:00","version":{"schema":0.796,"foundry":"10.291","system":"4.10.4"}}},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"common"},"level":{"value":0},"duration":{"value":-1,"unit":"unlimited","sustained":false,"expiry":"turn-start"},"start":{"value":0,"initiative":null},"target":null,"tokenIcon":{"show":false},"badge":null,"context":null,"unidentified":false},"img":"modules/drakkenheim-adventure-module-for-pathfinder-2nd-edition/artwork/icons/effects/Recharge_Icon.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.q2YrQFgawfzVFJpu"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.10.4","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1667016708223,"modifiedTime":1686957977853,"lastModifiedBy":"NZsmhzO5jgDe7jrT"},"ownership":{"default":0,"NZsmhzO5jgDe7jrT":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"MNslwavKd8BPJoX9"}
{"name":"Mutation","type":"effect","system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>In addition to suffering symptoms, each time a character gains a level of @UUID[Compendium.drakkenheim-adventure-module-for-pathfinder-2nd-edition.dodrakkenheim-effects.so17g2EB1xH8JzI9]{Contaminated}, it rolls [[/r {1d6}]]{1d6}. If the result is equal to or less than the creature's current level of Contamination the creature gains a mutation.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.835,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2023-06-12T11:43:26.206-04:00","version":{"schema":0.796,"foundry":"10.291","system":"4.10.4"}}},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"common"},"level":{"value":1},"duration":{"value":-1,"unit":"unlimited","sustained":false,"expiry":"turn-start"},"start":{"value":0,"initiative":null},"target":null,"tokenIcon":{"show":true},"badge":{"type":"counter","value":1},"context":null,"unidentified":false},"img":"modules/drakkenheim-adventure-module-for-pathfinder-2nd-edition/artwork/icons/effects/Mutation_Icon.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.mtlGDv7iuMdIjzgA"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.10.4","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1666929835294,"modifiedTime":1686957918660,"lastModifiedBy":"NZsmhzO5jgDe7jrT"},"ownership":{"default":0,"NZsmhzO5jgDe7jrT":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"W823JZGthJRu5zj4"}
{"name":"Spell Effect: Sanctified","type":"effect","system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>Granted by @UUID[Compendium.drakkenheim-adventure-module-for-pathfinder-2nd-edition.dodrakkenheim-spells.2DBrhgfCmfBP8u8r]{Sacrament of the Falling Fire}</p>\n<p><strong>You gain the following benefits so long as you adhere to the tenets and faith of the Falling Fire:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<div>You gain advantage on saving throws against being @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.9qGBRpbX9NEwtAAr]{Controlled} or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.TBSHQspnbcqxsmjL]{Frightened}, and resistance to negative and holy damage. </div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>You are immune to @UUID[Compendium.drakkenheim-adventure-module-for-pathfinder-2nd-edition.dodrakkenheim-effects.so17g2EB1xH8JzI9]{Contaminated}.</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>If you die, your soul enters the Delerium fragment embedded into your chest. You can't be raised from the dead while your soul is in the fragment.</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<p>The embedded Delerium fragment does not contaminate or otherwise harm a character who keeps their conviction.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.835,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2023-06-12T11:43:31.219-04:00","version":{"schema":0.796,"foundry":"10.291","system":"4.10.4"}}},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"common"},"level":{"value":9},"duration":{"value":-1,"unit":"unlimited","sustained":false,"expiry":"turn-start"},"start":{"value":0,"initiative":null},"target":null,"tokenIcon":{"show":true},"badge":null,"context":null,"unidentified":false},"img":"modules/drakkenheim-adventure-module-for-pathfinder-2nd-edition/artwork/icons/effects/Sanctified_Icon.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.iYcX2bOkNcVJMMvF"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.10.4","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1667512742895,"modifiedTime":1686958027004,"lastModifiedBy":"NZsmhzO5jgDe7jrT"},"ownership":{"default":0,"NZsmhzO5jgDe7jrT":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"aiImqshKiLAMGnt1"}
{"name":"Contaminated","type":"effect","system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>Exposure to eldritch pollutants within the Haze or arcane radiation emitted by delerium cause contamination, which inflicts both debilitating symptoms and otherworldy mutations.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Contamination is measured in six levels. An effect can give a creature one or more levels of contamination, as specified in the effect's description. If an already contaminated creature suffers another effect that causes further contamination, its current level of contamination increases by the amount specified in the effect's description. </p>\n<p>In addition, each time a character gains a full night's rest while they have one or more contamination levels, roll 1d20. On a 1, they gain a contamination level.</p>\n<p>Upon reaching contamination level 6 or higher, the creature transforms as described by @UUID[Compendium.drakkenheim-adventure-module-for-pathfinder-2nd-edition.dodrakkenheim-effects.GzQbOOQ3WxgcioOd]{Monstrous Transformation!}.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>In addition to suffering symptoms, each time a character gains a level of contamination, it rolls 1d6. If the result is equal to or less than the character's current contamination level the creature gains a @UUID[Compendium.drakkenheim-adventure-module-for-pathfinder-2nd-edition.dodrakkenheim-effects.W823JZGthJRu5zj4]{Mutation}.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Symptoms</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Level 1 </strong>None.</p>\n<p><strong>Level 2 </strong>All healing received reduced by half.</p>\n<p><strong>Level 3</strong> No Hit Points regained after resting.</p>\n<p><strong>Level 4</strong> Damage dealt by weapon attacks and spells halved.</p>\n<p><strong>Level 5</strong> Incapacitated</p>\n<p><strong>Level 6</strong> @UUID[Compendium.drakkenheim-adventure-module-for-pathfinder-2nd-edition.dodrakkenheim-effects.GzQbOOQ3WxgcioOd]{Monstrous Transformation!}</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.835,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2023-06-12T11:43:22.238-04:00","version":{"schema":0.796,"foundry":"10.291","system":"4.10.4"}}},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"common"},"level":{"value":1},"duration":{"value":-1,"unit":"unlimited","sustained":false,"expiry":"turn-start"},"start":{"value":0,"initiative":null},"target":null,"tokenIcon":{"show":true},"badge":{"type":"counter","value":1},"context":null,"unidentified":false},"img":"modules/drakkenheim-adventure-module-for-pathfinder-2nd-edition/artwork/icons/effects/Contaminated_Icon.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.20LAtbJCko5cQwND"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.10.4","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1666928451961,"modifiedTime":1686960790572,"lastModifiedBy":"vtXdnhFcs1Ab1ZZC"},"ownership":{"default":0,"NZsmhzO5jgDe7jrT":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"so17g2EB1xH8JzI9"}
{"name":"Spell Effect: Contaminated Power","type":"effect","system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>Granted by @UUID[Compendium.drakkenheim-adventure-module-for-pathfinder-2nd-edition.dodrakkenheim-spells.tNWMbrWilyd5hWNG]{Contaminated Power}</p>\n<p><strong>You gain the following benefits:</strong></p>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li>When you cast a spell that deals acid, fire, cold, lightning, or poison damage, you can change the damage type to force, negative, mental, or positive damage.</li>\n<li>Once per turn when you deal damage with a spell, you can deal an extra 1d12 negative damage for each @UUID[Compendium.drakkenheim-adventure-module-for-pathfinder-2nd-edition.dodrakkenheim-effects.so17g2EB1xH8JzI9]{Contaminated} level you have gained to one target of that spell.</li>\n<li>When you cast a spell that forces a creature to make a save to resist its effects, you can choose to gain one level of @UUID[Compendium.drakkenheim-adventure-module-for-pathfinder-2nd-edition.dodrakkenheim-effects.so17g2EB1xH8JzI9]{Contaminated}. If you do, one target of the spell must roll twice and take the lower number on its first saving throw made against that spell.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.835,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2023-06-12T11:43:33.375-04:00","version":{"schema":0.796,"foundry":"10.291","system":"4.10.4"}}},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"common"},"level":{"value":8},"duration":{"value":1,"unit":"minutes","sustained":false,"expiry":"turn-start"},"start":{"value":0,"initiative":null},"target":null,"tokenIcon":{"show":true},"badge":null,"context":null,"unidentified":false},"img":"modules/drakkenheim-adventure-module-for-pathfinder-2nd-edition/artwork/icons/effects/ContaminatedPower_Icon.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.H2jslhvUdSYDhDO5"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.10.4","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1667060641860,"modifiedTime":1686957998299,"lastModifiedBy":"NZsmhzO5jgDe7jrT"},"ownership":{"default":0,"NZsmhzO5jgDe7jrT":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"uuVxjz3edDxIdzka"}
